If I could describe Stackers in one word it would be "classic". It reminds me of that old show Cheers because literally everyone knows everyones name.   The beers cheap, the foods decent enough (which means its awesome when your slightly wasted) and the environments relaxed.... what else could you ask for in a bar??  Oh and yea, those 50 cent wings are some of the best in Phoenix,  try them!

