This mall blows... wait is it even a mall?? First off it's extreamly small, about 20 shops with those weird annoying little kiosks in the middle. Secondly almost all the shops in this lame mall are slightly hood/ghetto. I can count at least 3 stores in there that sell those weird baggy shirts with logos on them, gold chains and ecko pants.. Yea, those kind of stores...Third, it smells. Yes, it smells in there.. I'm not really sure what the smell is but its not a very good one.. There are a few decent things about this mall though which happen to be the food, theres a costco hot dog stand which has hot dogs and a soda for like a buck fifty, cant go wrong there.. Theres also a radioshack, gamestop, jcpenny and a Harkins theater.. but thats about it when it comes to good things about this mall.. AVOID THE WALMART at all costs! You'll wait in line for over an hour, its CRAZY!

